# Secrets and local credentials — never commit. The anonymity sweep (docs/RELEASING.md) checks
# that none of these leaked into a tracked file before any push.
*token*.txt
*.token
githubtoken.txt
forgejotoken.txt
.secrets/
.env
*.key
.cloudron.json

# Maintainer-private anonymity list (used by test/secret-scan.sh), never published.
.anonymize-list

# Editor and harness local state.
.claude/

# Local-only development and handoff docs. These carry box-specific context (the live test app
# hostname, the private mirror) that helps the next session continue but must never be published.
# The anonymized public record of what was verified lives in docs/PACKAGING-NOTES.md.
STATUS.md
RECON.md

# Local build, test, and scratch artifacts.
*.log
scratchpad/
tmp/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
